(129, 1, '2015-01-28 23:39:40', '2015-01-28 23:39:40', '<h2 style="text-align: center;">Despatch, Returns and Refunds Policy</h2>\r\n<strong>On Line Payment Options</strong>\r\n\r\nOn line payment are available by the following methods. PayPal, Visa and MasterCard. Bank transfer and cheque payments are acceptable and the order will be processed once funds as cleared in full. All amounts shown are in Australian Dollars (AUD).\r\n\r\n<strong>Dispatch and Delivery </strong>\r\n\r\nFree Delivery- Vic, NSW, Qld. Delivery charges applicable – SA, WA, NT and Tas. Please call 02 9832 0000.\r\n\r\nAll orders, after full payment received, will be dispatched from our warehouse within 2 business days for products in stock. Normal delivery is 3-4 business days after dispatch.\r\n\r\n(Western Australian and out laying areas may take longer). Delivery times are estimates only. If a product is out of stock, you will be contacted as to when the goods will be available.\r\n\r\n<strong>Returns</strong>\r\n\r\nAny goods to be returned must be re-saleable and the container unopened. All freight charges for returned stock are at the customer’s expense. Any returns must be accompanied with an issued credit number obtainable through our Customer Service department. Goods returned without a credit number will not be accepted. Tinted and made to order (MTO) goods are non-returnable. Returns must be completed within 30 days of sale invoice date. A 20% restock and handling fee will be charged on all returns.\r\n\r\n<strong>Refunds</strong>\r\n\r\nAny refundable monies will be credited via the method of payment received by the customer as per the sales invoice. We reserve the right to refund monies by whatever means are available. Dispatch, freight charges and handling are not refundable.\r\n\r\n<strong>Phone Orders</strong>\r\n\r\nYou may order by phone by calling Customer Service on (02) 9832 0000 weekdays between 8am to 5pm. (excludes public holidays).', 'Shopping Policy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'shopping-policy', '', '', '2015-03-18 07:02:36', '2015-03-18 07:02:36', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/PaintOnline/php/?page_id=129', 0, 'page', '', 0),
