(965, 1, '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '<strong>Industrial</strong>\r\n\r\nSince 1987,Omega Paints has built a profound reputation in the Surface Coatings Industry. Omega has always strived to engineer products to suit customers'' needs and has in its fold experienced lab technicians with advanced technology to cater to customer requirements.\r\n\r\nTo be the best in Quality and Services in the manufacture of high quality structural and industrial coatings, catering to the needs of industrial fabricators, equipment manufacturers, steel manufacturers, agricultural manufacturing and mining industries. Omega manufactures and supplies high quality industrial protective coating to a host of commercial and industrial clients as well as strives to deliver exceptional service and support to all customers at very competitive prices.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<strong>Decorative</strong>\r\n\r\nOur products are renowned for their quality and variety. With a wide range of decorative products, we guarantee that you will be arming yourself with the right options for any kind of painting purposes. Our Decorative products are perfect for your home decoration requirements. Whether you are looking for an exterior paint or paint for internal purposes, we have it all. From top quality washable acrylic interior paints, to weather blocking exterior paints, we have every area of your building covered.  Combined with the latest interior design ideas, our products can give you the best possible look for your home.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<strong>Driveway</strong>\r\n\r\nPainting your home with a fresh coat of paint and leaving the driveway and paths untouched, is like putting on a new outfit and wearing old shoes. We have products to protect and decorate any driveway or path area around you residence. Concrete Sealer, Paving Paint, Decking Finishes right up to industrial grade 2 pack epoxy and polyurethane coatings. Coatings that will not only bring your driveway and path back to life, but to protect them for years to come.\r\n\r\n<strong>Metal</strong>\r\n\r\nWith so much experience in quality industrial coating, we have recently released our products in a more DIY friendly range called Rustblock. Now you can use the same quality, hardwearing, long lasting products that in the past were only available to the metal engineering industry. The Rustblock range is available in spray cans, 1 litres and 4 litre sizes. Products such as Hammertone, Cold Galvanising, Epoxy Gloss Enamel and many other metal products are now at your disposal.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<strong>Pool</strong>\r\n\r\nIf you would like your pool to look inviting and refreshing all year through, Apco Coatings has just the right way to help you decorate and protect it, the Poolkote way. There are two types of coatings that are commonly used in the painting of pools: Chlorinated Rubber and solvent borne Epoxy (Two-Pack). Poolkote offers the two products in its range, both offering good looking and durability. So choose the right Poolkote product for your swimming pool and be assured of your enjoyment for years…and years! Poolkote offers you systems that cater to your specific needs.\r\n\r\n<strong>Road Marking</strong>\r\n\r\nRoad markings are the silent custodians of road safety in this era of four and six lane highways. Markings signify the delineation of traffic path and the lateral clearance from traffic hazard for the safe, smooth and orderly movement of traffic. Apart from traffic guidance, they also serve as a tool for controlling, warning and providing information to road users. APCO Coatings is one of the leading manufacturers and suppliers of road marking paints in Australia. At present we enjoy a large market share in supply of Water Based Road marking paint throughout Australia. Our road marking products range include fast drying highly durable 100% acrylic retro-reflective water borne paints, as well as conventional water / solvent based road marking paints.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<strong>Roof</strong>\r\n\r\nRoofs can be built from any number of strong building materials, but it’s the paint coating that ultimately protects the surface. It’s amazing that with just a couple of coats of APCO Highshield prevents damage of the roof’s surface from the sun’s harsh UV rays and punishing Australian weather. APCO Highshield is made in Australia for Australian conditions. So whatever type of roof you need to coat, cement tiles, galvanised iron, zincalume, etc, we have you covered.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<strong>Accessories</strong>\r\n\r\nWhether it’s re-painting a bedroom, revitalizing your timber deck, touching up some scuffed walls or a complete home re-paint, our paint accessories will help you achieve your painting task quickly and easily. We also have everything you need if you are painting the exterior of your house, from render roller sleeves, to extension poles for high surfaces and preparation products to get the job ready. Don’t forget we also have all of the safety and protective gear you will need to keep you safe when taking on your next painting job. ', 'News,tips & Advice', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'news-tips-advice', '', '', '2015-04-27 01:45:25', '2015-04-27 01:45:25', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/PaintOnline/php/?page_id=965', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(966, 1, '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '<b>APCO The Silent Custodians</b>\r\n\r\nRoad markings are the silent custodians of road safety in this era of four and six lane highways. Markings signify the delineation of traffic path and the lateral clearance from traffic hazard for the safe, smooth and orderly movement of traffic. Apart from traffic guidance, they also serve as a tool for controlling, warning and providing information to road users. Though the cost of road markings is fractional in comparison to the cost of the road, its importance is indisputable. Often a key parameter used to judge the road quality is the quality of the installed road marking.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Coatings Lead the Way</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Coatings is one of the leading manufacturers and suppliers of road marking paints in Australia. At present we enjoy a large market share in supply of Water Based Road marking paint throughout Australia. Our road marking products range include fast drying highly durable 100% acrylic retro-reflective water borne paints, as well as conventional water / solvent based road marking paints.\r\n\r\nAll road marking paints offered by APCO Coatings are manufactured at an AS/NZS ISO 9001:2008 quality endorsed manufacturing facility in Australia and all products are APAS approved.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO, In the thick of it</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Quickline road marking paints are suitable for delivering up to 600microns WFT, which is excellent for holding larger glass beads for better retro-reflectivity. APCO Quickline meets Australian Standards criteria of Fast Drying Paint requirements which is less than 5minutes drying time. The chief feature of this product is its faster drying time under at low temperature and high humidity environments. This product is extremely popular in cooler regional areas.\r\n\r\n<b>Would you like Water or Solvent with your order?</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Fast Dry Road Marking Paint is available in both water based as well as solvent based. They meet Australian Standards criteria for Fast Drying Paint which is less than 5 minutes drying time. APCO Fast Dry Road Marking paints are used in less demanding weather conditions in all areas of Australia. Suitable for building films up to 500 microns. Available in White, Yellow and a range of colours, these products are available in in 1,000 litres, 500 litres, 200 litres and 20 litres packs. No pick-up time for this product is between 4-5 minutes.\r\n\r\nAll road marking paints offered by APCO Coatings are manufactured at an AS/NZS ISO 9001:2008 quality endorsed manufacturing facility in Australia and all products are APAS approved.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Flying High</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Airpave: Airpave line marking paints are water based products, used for line marking runways, and taxi ways in airports. ʻAirpaveʼ paints also meet Australian Standards criteria for Fast Drying Paint which is less than 5minutes drying time. Airpave paints do not soften on environmental heat and hence dirt pickup is eliminated. Airpave paint offers excellent slip resistance and quick drying properties. Designed to Micro Layer Shear without leaving any film build which makes it an ideal choice for line marking runways, highways and apron / taxiways at airports.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Kicks for Gold</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Coatings also manufactures ʻSports Ovalʼ paints for line marking on grass sports fields and ovals. APCO Sports Oval Marking is an economical acrylic paint designed to provide high visibility and marking required for sports field marking and log marking. The product is easy to apply with good opacity, is water based and results in an easy to maintain flat finish.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Wins the Cup</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO AceKote Tennis Court / Sports Court Paint is 100% acrylic water based paint specifically formulated for tennis courts, basketball courts, volleyball courts and netball courts. The product offers a uniform non-slip finish as it is formulated with specially graded mineral fillers. Product is available with or without non slip aggregate to facilitate the application by spray.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Coatings a World Leader</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Coatings, the fastest growing paint company in the South Pacific and part of a large world-wide group of the best practice paint companies. The figures are hard to beat; operations in 20 countries, a turnover of over US$ 1 billion and a ranking in the world’s top ten paint companies.\r\n\r\nThe story begins with the international premier paint manufacturer, Asian Paints, its 60 year pedigree has seen the company named as one of the top six best managed companies in the country.\r\n\r\nAsian Paints as a company operates in 20 countries across the world. It has manufacturing facilities in each of these countries and is the largest paint company in nine overseas markets. Asian Paints operates in five regions across the world viz. South Asia, South East Asia, South Pacific, Middle East and Caribbean region through the four corporate brands.\r\n\r\n<b>Line Marking a concrete warehouse floor</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Fast Dry Solvent Based Road Marking is a chlorinated rubber modified alkyd based paint specifically designed for the application over asphalt, tar sealed substrates and concrete surfaces. The product dries fast and hence traffic hold up is minimum. Easy application and APCO Fast Dry Solvent Based Road Marking is available in commonly used marking colours.\r\n\r\n<b>A sealer so that tyre marks can be cleaned off the line marking</b>\r\n\r\nOnce the APCO Fast Dry Solvent Based Road Marking paint has dried, apply a coat of Omega Concrete Sealer Clear over the lines, this prevents the dirt and dust from the tyres from marking the lines, and makes it easy to clean.\r\n\r\n<b>Drying time of Waterborne Road Marking paints</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Road Marking Fast Dry Water Borne Paint dries very quickly and complies to the State and Federal Government Roads standards of No tyre pick up/marking dry time\r\n\r\nDrying Time (at 25C &amp; RH 60%)* (White N14): Less than 1 min 30 seconds. (Bright Yellow Y14): Less than 3 min.\r\n\r\nNote Cooler Temperatures, higher film thickness, low air flow conditions or higher humidity conditions will require longer drying time.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Road Marking Paint made in Australia</b>\r\n\r\nAll APCO Road Marking Paints made in Australia and manufactured in a Certified Facility with APAS, NATA and ISO 9001:2015.\r\n\r\n<b>APCO Coatings an Australian Company</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Coatings is a fully Australian Owned Company. The name brand APCO is one of the biggest coating companies internationally and is manufactured under licence by an Australian Company. This means that up to date world-wide technology is shared with our company.\r\n\r\n<b>Contact APCO Coatings Road Marking Division</b>\r\n\r\nAPCO Road Marking is available throughout Australia, simply contact our head office on 02 9832 0000 or e-mail at <a href="mailto:info@apcocoatings.com.au">info@apcocoatings.com.au</a> with your requirements.', 'News,tips & Advice', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '965-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '2015-02-18 08:40:07', '', 965, 'http://111.93.163.213/PaintOnline/php/965-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
